WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.401 line:80%
“The measure of intelligence is the ability to change.” - Albert Einstein

00:00:04.555 --> 00:00:09.881 line:80%
To be a successful entrepreneur, you must be flexible 
and open to making changes.

00:00:10.682 --> 00:00:16.421 line:80%
Often, you may need to pivot or change your initial idea 
or strategy to make your business work.

00:00:17.396 --> 00:00:20.396 line:80%
You may start by making assumptions about what needs to change, 

00:00:20.396 --> 00:00:25.639 line:80%
but you need to test these assumptions with real data before 
you actually pivot.

00:00:26.128 --> 00:00:28.199 line:80%
Ron has a cleaning service business.

00:00:28.668 --> 00:00:32.108 line:80%
For more than 10 years, it has been quite successful.

00:00:33.025 --> 00:00:37.744 line:80%
However in the past 6 months, the number of customers has declined.

00:00:39.001 --> 00:00:45.136 line:80%
Initially Ron thought customers were dissatisfied 
with the long waiting period before getting an appointment.

00:00:45.922 --> 00:00:49.610 line:80%
He decided to hire more people in order to provide a quick turnaround.

00:00:50.115 --> 00:00:51.785 line:80%
 However, this did not help.

00:00:52.308 --> 00:00:58.372 line:80%
Ron then decided to conduct a customer survey to better understand
 the problems faced by his customers.

00:00:59.264 --> 00:01:05.756 line:80%
 The results of his survey suggested that customers were dissatisfied
 with the process of calling and making appointments.

00:01:06.550 --> 00:01:11.920 line:80%
Most people preferred the convenience of using an app 
or website to schedule appointments,

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:15.920 line:80%
especially recurring ones, as well as for making payments.

00:01:16.132 --> 00:01:21.336 line:80%
Ron created an online presence for his business and soon his business 
picked up.